video_summary.description: Woo-hoo! TGI Monday—time to build my future with the power of work.
Fresh doughnuts in the break room? No time—work, work, work!
Only two people ahead—I'll be on top in no time.
Quitting time? Not yet—who are you really fooling?
What the... I hired that cone—I'm losing it!
When did I go from up-and-comer to beer drinker?
I used to have ambition, Moe. What took it away?
You start with huge dreams, then end up with a small ball of regrets.
I share your disappointment—you see, I never grew out of it.
